<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="<%= locale || 'en' %>">

<head>
    <%- include('partials/meta') %>
        <title>404 - Page Not Found | SyncTime</title>
        <meta name="description" content="The page you are looking for could not be found." />
        <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
        <style>
            .error-container {
                min-height: 60vh;
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: center;
                text-align: center;
                padding: 2rem;
            }

            .error-code {
                font-size: 8rem;
                font-weight: bold;
                color: var(--primary-color, #1f3c88);
                margin: 0;
                line-height: 1;
            }

            .error-title {
                font-size: 2rem;
                margin: 1rem 0;
                color: #333;
            }

            .error-description {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
                color: #666;
                max-width: 600px;
                margin: 1rem auto 2rem;
            }

            .error-actions {
                display: flex;
                gap: 1rem;
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                justify-content: center;
            }

            .error-btn {
                display: inline-block;
                padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
                border-radius: 6px;
                text-decoration: none;
                font-weight: 500;
                transition: all 0.3s ease;
            }

            .btn-primary {
                background-color: var(--primary-color, #1f3c88);
                color: white;
            }

            .btn-primary:hover {
                background-color: #152a5e;
                transform: translateY(-2px);
            }

            .btn-secondary {
                background-color: #f5f5f5;
                color: #333;
            }

            .btn-secondary:hover {
                background-color: #e0e0e0;
                transform: translateY(-2px);
            }

            .suggestions {
                margin-top: 3rem;
                padding: 2rem;
                background-color: #f9f9f9;
                border-radius: 8px;
                max-width: 800px;
            }

            .suggestions h3 {
                margin-top: 0;
                color: #333;
            }

            .suggestions ul {
                list-style: none;
                padding: 0;
                text-align: left;
            }

            .suggestions li {
                padding: 0.5rem 0;
            }

            .suggestions a {
                color: var(--primary-color, #1f3c88);
                text-decoration: none;
            }

            .suggestions a:hover {
                text-decoration: underline;
            }
        </style>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

        <main class="error-container">
            <h1 class="error-code">404</h1>

            <% if (locale==='ko' ) { %>
                <h2 class="error-title">페이지를 찾을 수 없습니다</h2>
                <p class="error-description">
                    요청하신 페이지가 존재하지 않거나 이동되었을 수 있습니다.
                    URL을 다시 확인해 주시거나, 아래 버튼을 통해 메인 페이지로 이동해 주세요.
                </p>

                <div class="error-actions">
                    <a href="/ko" class="error-btn btn-primary">🏠 메인으로 가기</a>
                    <a href="/ko/guide" class="error-btn btn-secondary">📖 가이드 보기</a>
                    <a href="/ko/contact" class="error-btn btn-secondary">📧 문의하기</a>
                </div>

                <div class="suggestions">
                    <h3>자주 찾는 페이지</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>🏠 <a href="/ko">메인 페이지</a> - 서버 시간 확인</li>
                        <li>📖 <a href="/ko/guide">이용 가이드</a> - SyncTime 사용 방법</li>
                        <li>📝 <a href="/ko/blog">블로그</a> - 티켓팅 팁 & 가이드</li>
                        <li>📊 <a href="/ko/trends">트렌드</a> - 인기 URL 통계</li>
                        <li>ℹ️ <a href="/ko/about">About</a> - SyncTime 소개</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <% } else if (locale==='jp' ) { %>
                    <h2 class="error-title">ページが見つかりません</h2>
                    <p class="error-description">
                        お探しのページは存在しないか移動した可能性があります。
                        URLを再確認するか、下のボタンからメインページに移動してください。
                    </p>

                    <div class="error-actions">
                        <a href="/jp" class="error-btn btn-primary">🏠 メインに戻る</a>
                        <a href="/jp/guide" class="error-btn btn-secondary">📖 ガイドを見る</a>
                        <a href="/jp/contact" class="error-btn btn-secondary">📧 お問い合わせ</a>
                    </div>

                    <div class="suggestions">
                        <h3>よく見るページ</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>🏠 <a href="/jp">メインページ</a> - サーバー時刻確認</li>
                            <li>📖 <a href="/jp/guide">利用ガイド</a> - SyncTimeの使い方</li>
                            <li>📝 <a href="/jp/blog">ブログ</a> - チケット購入のヒント</li>
                            <li>📊 <a href="/jp/trends">トレンド</a> - 人気URL統計</li>
                            <li>ℹ️ <a href="/jp/about">About</a> - SyncTime紹介</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <% } else if (locale==='zh-tw' ) { %>
                        <h2 class="error-title">找不到頁面</h2>
                        <p class="error-description">
                            您尋找的頁面不存在或已移動。
                            請重新確認URL，或透過下方按鈕前往主頁。
                        </p>

                        <div class="error-actions">
                            <a href="/zh-tw" class="error-btn btn-primary">🏠 返回主頁</a>
                            <a href="/zh-tw/guide" class="error-btn btn-secondary">📖 查看指南</a>
                            <a href="/zh-tw/contact" class="error-btn btn-secondary">📧 聯絡我們</a>
                        </div>

                        <div class="suggestions">
                            <h3>常用頁面</h3>
                            <ul>
                                <li>🏠 <a href="/zh-tw">主頁</a> - 伺服器時間確認</li>
                                <li>📖 <a href="/zh-tw/guide">使用指南</a> - 如何使用SyncTime</li>
                                <li>📝 <a href="/zh-tw/blog">部落格</a> - 售票技巧與指南</li>
                                <li>📊 <a href="/zh-tw/trends">趨勢</a> - 熱門URL統計</li>
                                <li>ℹ️ <a href="/zh-tw/about">About</a> - SyncTime介紹</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <% } else { %>
                            <h2 class="error-title">Page Not Found</h2>
                            <p class="error-description">
                                The page you are looking for does not exist or may have been moved.
                                Please check the URL again, or navigate back to the main page using the buttons below.
                            </p>

                            <div class="error-actions">
                                <a href="/en" class="error-btn btn-primary">🏠 Go to Home</a>
                                <a href="/en/guide" class="error-btn btn-secondary">📖 View Guide</a>
                                <a href="/en/contact" class="error-btn btn-secondary">📧 Contact Us</a>
                            </div>

                            <div class="suggestions">
                                <h3>Popular Pages</h3>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>🏠 <a href="/en">Home Page</a> - Check Server Time</li>
                                    <li>📖 <a href="/en/guide">Usage Guide</a> - How to use SyncTime</li>
                                    <li>📝 <a href="/en/blog">Blog</a> - Ticketing Tips & Guides</li>
                                    <li>📊 <a href="/en/trends">Trends</a> - Popular URL Statistics</li>
                                    <li>ℹ️ <a href="/en/about">About</a> - About SyncTime</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            <% } %>
        </main>

        <%- include('partials/footer') %>

</body>

</html>